5bf90","tid":1513872,"uid":300566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:34:55.000Z","msg":"其實點解我建議要留<br />\n係因為好多香港或者外國嘅留學生想留 又留唔到<br />\n雖然佢哋好喜歡澳洲 但冇辦法 一定要走<br />\n<br />\n你話佢好難得有機會留<br />\n點解唔留幾年 拎pr 再選擇？ <br />\n正常嚟講 好難先有噉嘅機會 可以留"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:38:31.000Z","msg":"投資移民囉<br />\n或者喺香港做幾年野有經驗唔係可以技術移民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人唔留幾年攞PR在選擇嘅原因係因為忍唔到想快啲返香港即係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20fe5514d1c8f898e8f84a2131293b57d43c203","tid":1513872,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"其實去到澳洲讀書屋企都有錢㗎啦<br />\n喺香港做幾年野投資咪得囉咁簡單<br />\n又或者技術移民又得"},{"pid":"b5a649a2bfb5dc103e1f17e1ba18080809dd3aaa","tid":1513872,"uid":307011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"拎左個居留權先！！<br />\n我有朋友又好似你咁，佢放棄左居留權，番到香港好後悔。。"},{"pid":"8050af13be36d67a3708951d7f5d58408fa23225","tid":1513872,"uid":109124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc21da217b31815c8ee054a4c311fd7b82638845","tid":1513872,"uid":40560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d33de882acc9b3694d6d77a338e4cf843b59fee","tid":1513872,"uid":109124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"年尾grad 猶豫緊留唔留 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"巴打讀咩科？屋企人點講呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2322e5a49f3ce5189be788bb06b4038091e82dc4","tid":1513872,"uid":170029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"好奇問你留低係用Grad visa 再博PR 定直接189 visa ?<br />\n<br />\n前者你搵到工先再考慮？<br />\n介唔介意講下你邊科？可以俾D經驗你<br />\n利申我417 -&gt; 457 -&gt; 189"},{"pid":"6e35c617601122af342a18af8f7ab05f573a7569","tid":1513872,"